            "Luxin Cannon": "<h2>Luxin Cannon</h2><p>\"Omnichrome\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Automatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 45</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 600</li><li>Damage: </li><li>Fire Rate: </li><li>Shot Speed: </li><li>Range: </li><li>Force: </li><li>Spread: </li><li>Notes: Fires laser shots at enemies. When the magazine is emptied the tip of the crystal will be launched for extra damage.</li></ul>",
