            "Moonscraper": "<h2>Moonscraper</h2><p>\"Beeeeoooowwww!\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Beam</li><li>Magazine Size: 500</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 500</li><li>Damage: 26</li><li>Fire Rate: 1</li><li>Shot Speed: ∞</li><li>Range: 50</li><li>Force: 20</li><li>Spread: 5</li><li>Notes: Fires a continuous laser that reflects when hitting anything solid for the first time.</li></ul>",
