            "Nail Gun": "<h2>Nail Gun</h2><p>\"Pest Control\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: D</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 500</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 500</li><li>Damage: 3</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.12</li><li>Shot Speed: 26</li><li>Range: 12</li><li>Force: 8</li><li>Spread: 10</li><li>Notes: Fires a rapid stream of low damage nails. Fires faster if fire button is rapidly tapped rather than held.</li></ul>",
