            "The Kiln": "<h2>The Kiln</h2><p>\"Fires Pots\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 8</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 200</li><li>Damage: </li><li>Fire Rate: </li><li>Shot Speed: </li><li>Range: </li><li>Force: </li><li>Spread: </li><li>Notes: Fires pots that break into 3 bouncing crystals upon hitting something.</li></ul>",
