            "Tear Jerker": "<h2>Tear Jerker</h2><p>\"Q_Q\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 20</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 100</li><li>Damage: </li><li>Fire Rate: </li><li>Shot Speed: </li><li>Range: </li><li>Force: </li><li>Spread: </li><li>Notes: Fires tears that leave behind puddles of water.</li></ul>",
            "Eye of the Beholster": "<h2>Eye of the Beholster</h2><p>\"What A Beauty!\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: B</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 12</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 250</li><li>Damage: 6</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.15</li><li>Shot Speed: 200</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 4</li><li>Spread: 4</li><li>Notes: The last shot of each clip spawns a friendly Beadie.</li></ul>",
            "Molotov Launcher": "<h2>Molotov Launcher</h2><p>\"Exactly What You Think\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 1</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 80</li><li>Damage: 6</li><li>Fire Rate: 1.5</li><li>Shot Speed: 18</li><li>Range: 35</li><li>Force: 13</li><li>Spread: 5</li><li>Notes: Fires molotovs that set areas on fire.</li></ul>",
            "Shock Rifle": "<h2>Shock Rifle</h2><p>\"Zap\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: B</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 15</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 250</li><li>Damage: 8</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.2</li><li>Shot Speed: 140</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 20</li><li>Spread: 5</li><li>Notes: Fires a zap of electricity.</li></ul>",
            "Bait Launcher": "<h2>Bait Launcher</h2><p>\"Meat Your Maker\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Charged</li><li>Magazine Size: 1</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 60</li><li>Damage: </li><li>Fire Rate: </li><li>Shot Speed: </li><li>Range: </li><li>Force: </li><li>Spread: </li><li>Notes: Fires a steak that causes a tiger to appear and maul the target.</li></ul>",
            "Brick Breaker": "<h2>Brick Breaker</h2><p>\"Wrong Kind Of Mortar\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 5</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 200</li><li>Damage: </li><li>Fire Rate: </li><li>Shot Speed: </li><li>Range: </li><li>Force: </li><li>Spread: </li><li>Notes: Fires turtle shells which pierce through enemies and bounce off of walls.</li></ul>",
            "Betrayer's Shield": "<h2>Betrayer's Shield</h2><p>\"Actually A Gun\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: B</li><li>Gun Type: Automatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 12</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 350</li><li>Damage: 6</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.1</li><li>Shot Speed: 23</li><li>Range: 18</li><li>Force: 12</li><li>Spread: 5</li><li>Notes: Upon reloading, leaves a protective shield on the ground. Players in that area will be protected until the shield has absorbed a number of bullets.</li></ul>",
            "Lower Case r": "<h2>Lower Case r</h2><p>\"Alphabetical!\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: D</li><li>Gun Type: Burst</li><li>Magazine Size: 36</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 900</li><li>Damage: 8</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.07</li><li>Shot Speed: 25</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 14</li><li>Spread: 0</li><li>Notes: Fires a burst of 6 bullets that spell out the word bullet.</li></ul>",
            "Excaliber": "<h2>Excaliber</h2><p>\"Once And Future\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: B</li><li>Gun Type: Burst</li><li>Magazine Size: 32</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 280</li><li>Damage: 7</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.15</li><li>Shot Speed: 26</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 15</li><li>Spread: 0</li><li>Notes: Fires a burst of three piercing sword projectiles. Reloading swings the sword, destroying nearby bullets. Increases curse while held.</li></ul>",
            "Face Melter": "<h2>Face Melter</h2><p>\"Squiddley-squiddley-wheeyooo!\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: B</li><li>Gun Type: Automatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 60</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 300</li><li>Damage: 3</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.1</li><li>Shot Speed: 15</li><li>Range: 15</li><li>Force: 13</li><li>Spread: 6</li><li>Notes: Simultaneously fires music notes in four directions. Places an amplifier on the ground at the player's position upon reloading. Whenever the Face Melter is fired, the amplifier will fire music notes in the same pattern. Reloading again will remove the amplifier and place a new one.</li></ul>",
            "Trident": "<h2>Trident</h2><p>\"Under The Sea\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: A</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 6</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 250</li><li>Damage: 8</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.08</li><li>Shot Speed: 600</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 4</li><li>Spread: 0</li><li>Notes: Fires a long-range laser that pierces one enemy.</li></ul>",
            "Abyssal Tentacle": "<h2>Abyssal Tentacle</h2><p>\"Look Away\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: A</li><li>Gun Type: Beam</li><li>Magazine Size: 500</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 500</li><li>Damage: 22.5</li><li>Fire Rate: 1</li><li>Shot Speed: ∞</li><li>Range: 30</li><li>Force: 10</li><li>Spread: 0</li><li>Notes: Fires a tentacle that homes in on and grips enemies, damaging them.</li></ul>",
            "Quad Laser": "<h2>Quad Laser</h2><p>\"No One Can Defeat It\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 1</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 50</li><li>Damage: </li><li>Fire Rate: </li><li>Shot Speed: </li><li>Range: </li><li>Force: </li><li>Spread: </li><li>Notes: Fires a large, square bullet that moves extremely slowly.</li></ul>",
            "Pitchfork": "<h2>Pitchfork</h2><p>\"Get Forked!\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 200</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 200</li><li>Damage: 4</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.15</li><li>Shot Speed: 23</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 35</li><li>Spread: 5</li><li>Notes: Fires fireballs that have a chance to Burn enemies.</li></ul>",
            "Gungeon Ant": "<h2>Gungeon Ant</h2><p>\"What Army?\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 6</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 100</li><li>Damage: 22</li><li>Fire Rate: 0</li><li>Shot Speed: 26</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 25</li><li>Spread: 0</li><li>Notes: Reloading alternates between firing spreads of bullets that leave behind oil and flaming bullets.</li></ul>",
            "Alien Engine": "<h2>Alien Engine</h2><p>\"The Dangerzone\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: B</li><li>Gun Type: Automatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 1000</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 1000</li><li>Damage: 10</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.02</li><li>Shot Speed: 30</li><li>Range: 3</li><li>Force: 10</li><li>Spread: 0</li><li>Notes: Rapid fire weapon that has a very short range, only damaging enemies that come into contact with the muzzle flash. Enemies damaged have a chance to catch on fire. Extremely high recoil.</li></ul>",
