            "Bee Hive": "<h2>Bee Hive</h2><p>\"Bzzzzzzz!\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: B</li><li>Gun Type: Automatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 300</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 300</li><li>Damage: 3</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.1</li><li>Shot Speed: 9</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 2</li><li>Spread: 90</li><li>Notes: Fires bees that home in on and damage enemies.</li></ul>",
            "Silencer": "<h2>Silencer</h2><p>\"300 Dead Count\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: C</li><li>Gun Type: Semiautomatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 8</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 200</li><li>Damage: 13</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.6</li><li>Shot Speed: 23</li><li>Range: 60</li><li>Force: 30</li><li>Spread: 5</li><li>Notes: Fires zippers. Hitting an enemy with the swing of the weapon will stun the enemy.</li></ul>",
