            "Cactus": "<h2>Cactus</h2><p>\"1000 Needles!\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: </li><li>Gun Type: Automatic</li><li>Magazine Size: 1000</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 1000</li><li>Damage: </li><li>Fire Rate: </li><li>Shot Speed: </li><li>Range: </li><li>Force: </li><li>Spread: </li><li>Notes: Fires needles.</li></ul>",
            "Black Hole Gun": "<h2>Black Hole Gun</h2><p>\"Won't You Come\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: A S</li><li>Gun Type: Charged</li><li>Magazine Size: 1</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 30</li><li>Damage: 10</li><li>Fire Rate: 1</li><li>Shot Speed: 4</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 9</li><li>Spread: 0</li><li>Notes: Fires black holes that attract enemies and enemy bullets.</li></ul>",
            "BSG": "<h2>BSG</h2><p>\"Big Shooty Gun\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: S</li><li>Gun Type: Charged</li><li>Magazine Size: 1</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 25</li><li>Damage: 6</li><li>Fire Rate: 4</li><li>Shot Speed: 25</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 10</li><li>Spread: 0</li><li>Notes: Slowly charges up to fire a large high-damage projectile.</li></ul>",
            "Compressed Air Tank": "<h2>Compressed Air Tank</h2><p>\"You Know My Work\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: A</li><li>Gun Type: Charged</li><li>Magazine Size: 1</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 50</li><li>Damage: 50</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.6</li><li>Shot Speed: 35</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 60</li><li>Spread: 6</li><li>Notes: Fires sharks that swim around the room, seeking enemies and biting them.</li></ul>",
            "Serious Cannon": "<h2>Serious Cannon</h2><p>\"Seriously MENTAL\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: A</li><li>Gun Type: Charged</li><li>Magazine Size: 1</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 30</li><li>Damage: 50</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.6</li><li>Shot Speed: 35</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 60</li><li>Spread: 6</li><li>Notes: Fires large bouncing cannonballs.</li></ul>",
            "Makeshift Cannon": "<h2>Makeshift Cannon</h2><p>\"You Only Get One Shot\"</p><ul><li>Gun Quality: S</li><li>Gun Type: Charged</li><li>Magazine Size: 1</li><li>Ammo Capacity: 1</li><li>Damage: 50</li><li>Fire Rate: 0.5</li><li>Shot Speed: 35</li><li>Range: 1000</li><li>Force: 60</li><li>Spread: 6</li><li>Notes: Fires a single blast that deals a large amount of damage.</li></ul>",
            "Master Round I": "<h2>Master Round I</h2><p>\"First Chamber\"</p><ul><li>Item Quality: N</li><li>Item Type: Passive</li><li>Notes: Grants a heart container.</li></ul>",
